{"service_name": "Methods Advisory: Sourcing and Procurement Consultancy", "service_id": "7189086793347833", "company_name": "Methods Advisory Ltd", "page_content": "<main id=\"content\" role=\"main\">\n <div class=\"grid-row\">\n  <div class=\"column-two-thirds\">\n   <header class=\"page-heading-smaller\">\n    <p class=\"context\">\n     Methods Advisory Ltd\n    </p>\n    <h1>\n     Methods Advisory: Sourcing and Procurement Consultancy\n    </h1>\n   </header>\n  </div>\n </div>\n <div class=\"grid-row\">\n  <div class=\"column-two-thirds\">\n   <p class=\"service-summary-lede\">\n    Methods Advisory delivers end-to-end procurement support consultancy, from a turnkey solution, including full procurement management, to providing selected specialist sourcing support to help you along the procurement timeline. We are fully conversant with all types of procurement process and EU Directives (including 2015 changes) and procuring through Government CCS Frameworks.\n   </p>\n   <h2 class=\"service-summary-heading\">\n    Features\n   </h2>\n   <ul class=\"service-summary-features-and-benefits\">\n    <li>\n     Full familiarity and experience of the HMT \u201cFive Case\u201d model\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Creating content that will survive CCS Gateway/ Tollgate scrutiny/ audit\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Clarification and quantification of estimated costs, risks and expected benefits\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Quality assurance of business case content and/or process\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Applicable to both commissioning and decommissioning of assets or services\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Supports embedding the business case as a central Programme control\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Approach is scalable to the size/ risk of the investment\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Uses experienced and qualified staff, including CCS Gateway Reviewers\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Templated and proven models for options, finance and benefits analysis\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Applicable across all types of public service organisation\n    </li>\n   </ul>\n   <h2 class=\"service-summary-heading\">\n    Benefits\n   </h2>\n   <ul class=\"service-summary-features-and-benefits\">\n    <li>\n     Lowers development cost through re-use of models and common content\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Stronger scenario and impact modelling\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Less business case over-engineering through a managed risk approach\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Increased commitment from Business Managers through effective process change approach\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Improved benefits management by creating a robust baseline for measurement\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     More accurate organisational confidence level through delivery and sustainability assessment\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Improved governance to support continued alignment to business case objectives\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Increased transparency makes business case a key communication tool\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Increases knowledge transfer through shared learning and related external content\n    </li>\n   </ul>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"column-one-third\">\n   <div id=\"meta\">\n    <h2 class=\"visuallyhidden\">\n     Pricing\n    </h2>\n    <p class=\"price\">\n     \u00a3300 per person per day\n    </p>\n    <ul class=\"price-caveats\">\n     <li>\n      Excluding VAT\n     </li>\n     <li>\n      Minimum contract period: Day\n     </li>\n    </ul>\n    <h2 class=\"visuallyhidden\">\n     Service documents\n    </h2>\n    <ul class=\"document-list\">\n     <li class=\"document-list-item\">\n      <a class=\"document-link-with-icon\" href=\"https://assets.digitalmarketplace.service.gov.uk/g-cloud-7/documents/92308/7189086793347833-pricing-document-2015-09-28-1034.pdf\">\n       <span class=\"document-icon\">\n        pdf\n        <span>\n         document:\n        </span>\n       </span>\n       Pricing\n      </a>\n     </li>\n     <li class=\"document-list-item\">\n      <a class=